com.acrolinx.javasdk.gui

Class PresenterFactoryImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.acrolinx.javasdk.gui.PresenterFactoryImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PresenterFactory

    public class PresenterFactoryImpl
extends Object
implements PresenterFactory
    A PresenterFactoryImpl creates the presenter used for presenting views provided by ViewFactory. This class will be used by DialogsPresenter.
